summary: There’s apparently a scene in the art room at Peter’s high school, SUNFLOWERS from Spiderverse may be on the Far From Home...
body:
There’s apparently a scene in the art room at Peter’s high school, SUNFLOWERS from Spiderverse may be on the Far From Home soundtrack, and Chris Evans is casted to appear in it. Which leads me to my three predictions:

  1. The return of Captain America PSA’s
  2. Old Steve becomes the art teacher at Peter’s high school
  3. Old Steve compliments Miles on his spray painted murals on his way home in Brooklyn

Any of which would be wholesome.

^Art room

summary:
Friendly Neighborhood Spider-Man #3  Writer:  J. Michael Straczynski, Pencils:  Mike Wieringo

  He stands like a vampire over...
caption:
Friendly Neighborhood Spider-Man #3 Writer: J. Michael Straczynski, Pencils: Mike Wieringo

He stands like a vampire over the bed. Mouths open on the palms of his hands and he lowers them to Peter’s helpless body. In consuming Peter he will take all his strength and all his power, everything Peter is, has been or could become, will be Morlun.

But Peter is not without his protector. At the very last moment, Mary Jane bursts into the room and tackles Morlun. “Leave him alone!” she yells, gouging at his eyes with her fingernails. –SpiderFan.org
